{"tid":1172224,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［估司機］觀塘道私家車剷巴士站撞人群　釀1死6傷","createTime":"2019-05-26T09:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T16:24:26.000Z","uid":28245,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"eda24549074b22a6b23f88b5b08badf899d7ada6","tid":1172224,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:42:42.000Z","msg":"牛頭角發生嚴重交通意外，今日(26日)下午近3時，一輛私家車沿觀塘道往觀塘方向行駛，駛至牛頭角下邨對開，懷疑天雨路滑失控剷上巴士站，撞倒4名途人，撞爛巴士站廣告燈箱後，再180度掉頭，撞及巴士站牌始停下，私家車安全氣袋彈出，消防接報到場展開救援，警方封鎖現場調查。現場消息稱，私家車女司機和2名乘客、以及4名途人共7人受傷。及至下午4時許，私家車上一名男乘客送院後證實不治。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190526/mobile/bkn-20190526150601406-0526_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190526%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190526150601406-0526_00822_001.html&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18Bf8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=b48f29cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190526/mobile/bkn-20190526150601406-0526_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7fdebb72410ea45c4197aa0b20b0c793f151bee0","tid":1172224,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8c07aaed47901c54897dab6be84a570ec72282","tid":1172224,"uid":22224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"雙袋本田jazz仔<br />\nRip....."},{"pid":"208c6ccf3f91a721234387922c8a62a0a4e0ea8f","tid":1172224,"uid":135867,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果個位無遮無掩"},{"pid":"26d3d9292a9eab11accf039cee41c684943c7b32","tid":1172224,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"208c6ccf3f91a721234387922c8a62a0a4e0ea8f","t